DB Tables:

User Info Table :
    UID*, Name, Money, LVL, EXP, HP, MP, STAM, ATK, DEF, EqpdItem

Battle Table :
    UID*, playerHP, playerMP, playerSTAM, playerATK, playerDEF, playerEqpdItem, enemyHP, enemyMP, enemySTAM, enemyATK, enemyDEF

Spell Table:
    UID*, KnownSpell1, KnownSpell2, etc.

Inventory Table:
    UID*, Object 1, Object 2, etc.



Encounters:
    1 - Enter combat with a randomized monster adjusted to your level. If you win, you get EXP and loot.
